# OMEGA System Master Gitignore (Root)

# --- Dependencies ---
**/node_modules/
**/vendor/
.pnpm-store/

# --- Next.js (Admin & Client) ---
# Ignore build output and cache for all Next.js apps
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/

# --- Laravel (API) ---
# Ignore storage, keys, and local configuration
api/storage/*.key
api/.phpunit.result.cache
api/public/storage
api/public/hot

# --- Environment Secrets (CRITICAL) ---
# Never commit local environment files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.production
!**/.env.example

# --- Tooling & Debug ---
.playwright-cli/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*
**/.eslintcache

# --- Operating System Files ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db